[{"Id": 1013248, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": 1, "EnglishDescription": "The author of Mustadrak has reported from the book of Mazar by Muhammad ibn Mashhadi that Imam Sadiq (a) visited the head of Imam Husain (a) while he was at the head’s side of the tomb of Imam Ali (a) where he offered 4 rakat namaz and said the following form of Ziyarat…", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Mustadrak ke raawi, kitaab al-Mazar jo Muhammad ibne Mashhadi ki hai, woh farmate hai keh jab Imam Sadiq (a), Imam Husain (a) ke sar ki ziyarat karna chahte to qabre Imam Ali (a) ke sarhaane (head side) khade ho kar 4 rakat namaz adaa karte thay aur phir is tarah se kehte…", "UrduDescription": "مستدرک میں محمد ابن مشہدی کی کتاب مزار سے نقل کیا گیا ہے کہ امام جعفر صادق ؑ نے امیر المومنینؑ کے سرہانے کی طرف امام حسینؑ کے سر کی زیارت پڑھی اور اس کے قریب ۴ رکعت نماز ادا فرمائی۔۔۔", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10