ll, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1013249, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "Peace be on you, O the son of the Messenger of Allah. Peace be on you, O the son of Amir Al-Momeneen. Peace be on you, O the son of the most truthful thoroughly purified chief of the women of the worlds. Peace be on you, O my master, Aba Abdillah, and also mercy and benedictions of Allah.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Aap par salaam ho ay Rasool'e Khuda (s.a.w.a) ke farzand. Aap par salaam ho ay Ameerul Momeneen (a.s) ke farzand. Aap par salaam ho ay Siddiqa Tahera ke farzand jo jahano ki aurto’n ki sardaar hai. Aap par salaam ho ay mere Maula, ay Abu Abdillah (a.s). Khuda ki rehmat ho aur Uski barkate’n ho.", "Urdu": "آپ پر سلام ہو اے رسولِؐ خدا کے فرزند! آپ پر سلام ہو اے امیر المومنین ؑکے فرزند! آپ پر سلام ہو اے صدیقہ طاہرہ کے فرزند جو جہانوں کی عورتوں کی سردار ہیں سلام ہوآپ پر اے میرے مولا اے ابوعبد ؑاللہ! خدا کی رحمت ہو اور اس کی برکتیں ہوں۔", "RArabic": "AS-SALAAMO A’LAIKA YABNA RASOOLIL LAAHE AS-SALAAMO A’LAIKA YABNA AMEERIL MOMENEENA AS-SALAAMO A’LAIKA YABNAS SIDDEEQATIT TAAHERATE SAYYEDATE NESAAA-IL A’ALAMEEN AS-SALAAMO A’LAIKA YAA MAWLAAYA YAA ABAA A’BDIL LAAHE WA RAHMATUL LAAHE WA BARAKAATOHU.", "ArabicText1": "اَسَّلَامُ عَلَیْكَ یَابْنَ رَسُوْلِ اللهِ۔ اَسَّلَامُ عَلَیْكَ یَابْنَ اَمِیْرِ الْمُؤْمِنِیْنَ۔ اَسَّلَامُ عَلَیْكَ یَابْنَ الصِّدِّیْقَۃِ الطَّاهِرَۃِ سَیِّدَۃِ نِسَآئِ الْعٰالَمِیْنَ۔ اَسَّلَامُ عَلَیْكَ یَا مَوْلَایَ یَا اَبَا عَبْدِ اللهِ وَ رَحْمَۃُ اللهِ وَبَرَكَاتُهٗ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1013250, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "I bear witness that verily you had established salaat, gave zakaat, advised people to do good and abstain from evil, recited the Holy Qur’an as it should have been recited, strived in the way Allah as it should have been done, exercised self control in the midst of hardships, till that which is certain (death) came to you.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Mai gawahi deta hu keh yaqeenan aap ne namaz qaaem ki aur zakaat adaa farmaayi, aap ne neki karne ka hukm diya aur buraayi se mana kiya, aap ne tilaawat’e Qur’an ka haq adaa kiya aur Khuda ki raah mein jehaad ka haq adaa kiya, us mein aap ne aziyat par sabr kiya islaahe haal ke khaatir hatta keh shahadat qabool kar li.", "Urdu": "میں گواہی دیتا ہوں کہ یقینًا آپ نے نماز قائم کی اور زکوٰۃ ادا فرمائی آپ نے نیکی کرنے کا حکم دیا اور برائی سے منع کیا آپ نے تلاوتِ قرآن کا حق ادا کیا اور خدا کی راہ میں جہاد کا حق ادا کیا اس میں آپ نے اذیت پر صبر کیا اصلاح ِحال کی خاطر حتیٰ کہ شہادت قبول کر لی۔", "RArabic": "ASH-HADO ANNAKA QAD AQAMTAS SALAATA WA AATAYTAZ ZAKAATA WA AMARTA BIL MA’ROOFE WA NAHAYTA A’NIL MUNKARE WA TALAWTAL KETAABA HAQQA TELAAWATEHI WA JAAHADTA FIL LAAHE HAQQA JEHAADEHI WA SABARTA A’LAL AZAA FEE JAMBEHI MOHTASEBAN HATTAA ATAAKAL YAQEENO.", "ArabicText1": "اَشْهَدُ اَنَّكَ قَدْ اَقَمْتَ الصَّلٰوۃَ وَاٰتَیْتَ الزَّكٰوۃَ وَاَمَرْتَ بِالْمَعْرُوْفِ وَنَهَیْتَ عَنِ الْمُنْكَرِ وَ تَلَوْتَ الْكِتَابَ حَقَّ تِلَاوَتِهٖ وَجَاهَدْتَ فِی اللهِ حَقَّ جِهَادِهٖ وَصَبَرْتَ عَلَی الْاَذٰی فِیْ جَنْبِهٖ مُحْتَسِبًا حَتّٰی اَتٰیكَ الْیَقِیْنُ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1013251, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "I bear witness that verily those who opposed you, waged war against you, and those who abandoned you, killed you, had been cursed and condemned by the Holy Prophet. He who invented a lie against you had been wiped out. May Allah curse those tyrants who oppressed you, whether they were those who initiated the injustice or those who completed it, may Allah increase their terrible punishment.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Aur mai gawahi deta hu keh be-shak jinho ne aap ki mukhaalefat ki, aap se jang ki jinho ne aap ki nusrat na ki aur jinho ne aap ko qabool kiya woh Nabiye Ummi ke farmaan ke mutaabiq maloon thaiyraahe gaye hai aur jis ne aap par bohtaan baandha woh ruswa huwa. Khuda ki laanat ho awwaleen o aakhereen par jinho ne aap par zulm dhaaya unke dard-naak azaab mein izaafa hota chala jaaye.", "Urdu": "اور میں گواہی دیتا ہوں کہ بے شک جنہوں نے آپ کی مخالفت کی آپ سے جنگ کی جنہوں نے آپ کی نصرت نہ کی اور جنہوں نے آپ کو قتل کیا وہ نبیؐ امی کے فرمان کے مطابق ملعون ٹھہرائے گئے ہیں اور جس نے آپ پر بہتان باندھا وہ رسو اہوا خدا کی لعنت ہو اولین و آخرین پر جنہوں نے آپ پر ظلم ڈھایا ان کے دردناک عذاب میں اضافہ ہوتاچلا جائے۔", "RArabic": "WA ASH-HADO ANNAL LAZEENA KHAALAFOOKA WA HAARABOOKA WA ANNAL LAZEENA KHAZALOOKA WAL LAZEENA QATALOOKA MAL-O’ONOONA A’LAA LESAANIN NABIYYIL UMMIYYE WA QAD KHAABA MANIF TARAA LA-A’NAL LAAHUZ ZAALEMEENA LAKUM MENAL AWWALEENA WAL AAKHEREENA WA ZAA-A’FA A’LAIHEMUL A’ZAABAL ALEEMA ATAYTOKA.", "ArabicText1": "وَاَشْهَدُ اَنَّ الَّذِیْنَ خَالَفُوْكَ وَحَارَبُوْكَ وَاَنَّ الَّذِیْنَ خَذَلُوْكَ وَالَّذِیْنَ قَتَلُوْكَ مَلْعُوْنُوْنَ عَلٰی لِسَانِ النَّبِیِّ الْاُ مِّیِّ وِقَدْخَابَ مَنِ افْتَرٰی لَعْنَ اللهُ الظَّالِمِیْنَ لَكُمْ مِنَ الْاَوَّلِیْنَ وَالْاٰخِرِیْنَ وَضَاعَفْ عَلَیْهِمُ الْعَذَابَ الْاَلِیْمَ اَتَیْتُكَ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1013252, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "I am here of my master, O son of the Messenger of Allah as your zair, aware of your rights, I am a friend of your friends, I am an enemy of your enemies. I am aware of the right path on which you had always walked, I know well that those who opposed you had gone astray, so recommend my case to your Lord. Peace be on you, and also mercy and benedictions of Allah.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Ay mere Maula, ay Rasool’e Khuda (s.a.w.a) ke farzand, mai aap ki ziayart ko aaya hu, aap ke haq ko pehchaanta hu, aap ke dosto’n ka dost, aap ke dushmano ka dushman hu, us hidaayat ko haq samajh-ta hu jis ko aap ne ikhteyaar kiya, aap ke mukhaalifo’n ki gumraahi se waaqif hu, pas apne Rab ke yahan meri shafa’at farmaaye.", "Urdu": "اے میرے مولا اے رسولؐ خدا کے فرزند! میں آپ کی زیارت کو آیا ہوں آپ کے حق کو پہچانتا ہوں آپ کے دوستوں کا دوست آپ کے دشمنوں کا دشمن ہوں اس ہدایت کو حق سمجھتا ہوں جس کو آپ نے اختیار کیا آپ کے مخالفوں کی گمراہی سے واقف ہوں۔ پس اپنے رب کے ہاں میری شفاعت فرمائیں۔", "RArabic": "YAA MAWLAAYA YABNA RASOOLIL LAAHE ZAAA-ERAN A’AREFAN BE HAQQEKA MOWAALEYAN LE AWLEYAAA-EKA MO-A’ADEYAN LE A-A’DAAA-EKA MUSTABSERAN BIL HODAL LAZEE ANTA A’LAIHE A’AREFAN BE ZALAALATE MAN KHAALAFAKA FASH-FA’ LEE I’NDA RABBEKA.", "ArabicText1": "یَا مَوْلَایَ یَابْنَ رَسُوْلِ اللهِ زَائِرًا عَارِفًا بِحَقِّكَ مُوَالِیًا لِّاَوْلِیَآئِكَ مُعَادِیًا لَّاِعْدَائِكَ مُسْتَبْصِرًا بِالْهُدَی الَّذِیْ اَنْتَ عَلَیْهِ عَارِفًا بِضَلَالَۃِ مَنْ خَالَفَكَ فَاشْفَعْ لِیْ عِنْدَ رَبِّكَ وَالسَّلَامُ عَلَیْكَ وَرَحْمَۃُ اللهِ وَبَرَكَاتُهٗ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null,